# Rockchip DRM

- Get pixelclk-active and de-active from drm_mode_flags
  This requires to update drm_display_mode_from_videomode() in drm_modes.c

  cf. Documentation/devicetree/bindings/video/display-timing.txt
      of_parse_display_timing() in drivers/video/of_display_timing.c

  flags DISPLAY_FLAGS_PIXDATA_POSEDGE / DISPLAY_FLAGS_PIXDATA_NEGEDGE
        DISPLAY_FLAGS_DE_HIGH / DISPLAY_FLAGS_DE_LOW

  in struct display_timing *dt->flags

- Win1 as cursor plane

- Win1 as overlay plane

- IRQ handle vblank events / page flips


